# Tech Stack Overview

This project uses a modern web development stack with the following key components:

## Frontend
- React with TypeScript for type-safe UI development
- Vite for fast development and optimized builds
- Tailwind CSS for utility-first styling
- PWA support for offline capabilities

## Backend
- Node.js + Express REST API
- MongoDB for data storage
- Docker for containerization
- PM2 for process management
- Nginx as reverse proxy

## DevOps & Infrastructure
- Ubuntu Server for hosting
- UFW for firewall management
- Let's Encrypt for SSL/TLS
- Fail2Ban for security
- Dynamic DNS support for home hosting

## External APIs
- Sunrise/Sunset data from sunrise-sunset.org
- Moon phase data from farmsense.net
- Timezone data from worldtimeapi.org
- Solar activity data from NOAA
- Schumann Resonance data from HeartMath

## Monitoring
- Uptime Kuma for availability monitoring
- Netdata for system metrics
- Logrotate for log management

